cross: Cymbidium First Dance x Cymbidium Shanghai Spots

measurements.description: Eighteen flowers on one 67-cm arched inflorescence, measured to the terminal flower; sepals and petals cream flushed dark dusty rose, spotted dark purple-maroon overall, spots coalesced at midrib of petals; lip intense dark maroon, edged cream, keels yellow spotted dark maroon; column cream, spotted dark maroon, anther cap maroon; substance firm; texture satin, lip velvet.
